Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance between the Secret and the Scub Coral is 4km.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Georg, what type is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.17,0:01:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Working on it, Miss Hallstrom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I am currently retrieving data from HQ's database,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's very similar to the one that \Nappeared in South America in the 1940s.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are very few photographs from that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.81,0:01:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so the records are mostly based on the descriptions of survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.45,0:01:52.63,Alt,,0,0,0,,Estimated time of arrival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:54.80,Alt,,0,0,0,,Eleven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Secret will reach the Scub Coral in eight minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, there will be a humongous Scub Burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too late if we dispatch after we arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard Fleur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Elena?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:14.80,Alt,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Okinawan SDF is scrambling. We can't contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice because we don't have a contract yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all countries, they should know best.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not handing it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not handing it over to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.07,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to take advantage of you in the confusion of the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You were born on this island like us, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to just stand there and watch the island get destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:02.19,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\pos(95,175)}{\fad(0,1000)\fscx70}CALL IT WHAT YOU WANT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a message to the Japanese Army carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You are trespassing on the territory of the United Okinawan Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No answer... Fucking Japs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We just received orders to oversee the arrival of Generation Bleu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The international rescue team, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They're telling us to let the Japs go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years later, a Scub Burst happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Japs choose this time to trespass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me this is just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have time to bother with us, do you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the Secret makes contact with the Scub Coral,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not going to get away unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you have no objections. We are leaving these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.97,0:04:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The G-Monster is leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the key of an army FP?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The Japs are looking for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I want to get their help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are from the enemy nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're not going to help, jack the FP and get rid of the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Scub Coral?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've seen it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they teaching you in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Monsters emerge from Scub Bursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're demons that will destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But the international rescue team will do something about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if they don't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what do you have in mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I honestly don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we don't do anything, the island will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, the Japs are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No surprise there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Han! How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.12,0:05:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.94,0:05:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've estimated their course with help from the Okinawan ships' that turned back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sending it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Secret should be moving toward the Scub Coral!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it coming after us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Two unknown FPs are closing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They are the smugglers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you want to land on a moving ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference in velocity is too big!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch and learn. This is how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I didn't know you could use the FP's anchors like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys... I think they're aiming something at us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! They have the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They were just warning shots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The Secret has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it seems to be pointing its main cannon at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Shit! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Holy shit! Holy shit! Holy fucking shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,God dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Break the glass!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An FP?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in it! Get in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Jap FP! Get in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop whining! You have the key, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's gonna do it if you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It has power and it's running. I've got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The controls are pretty much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be fine. It'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I must protect the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Arata family...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have to say, our country is shit out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I should hurry or I'll end up sinking before I could even—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're synchronizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.95,0:09:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome... Welcome home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Eureka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? Why did it suddenly activate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this tremor... The Mark I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it! The brat did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's gonna save us then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a discount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Secret's not accelerating or changing its direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Okinawan SDF is not responding either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Halstrom, there seems to be an error in detection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,An error? What error?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The identification code of the IFO that is rapidly nearing in on the Secret
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is identical to the Mark I, which was withdrawn from action last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It has shoulders?  Wait, this is an IFO?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do this... I can do this... I can do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't even found Ao yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Ao that I'll be at the Central Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine you'd be helping us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you helped that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The island changed when she came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She brought misfortune and pain upon this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't involve the children in this any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The son of that woman, Ao, is also a child of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I must do something... I must do something... I must do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you returned? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Help them! There's Japanese blood inside all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Generation Bleu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Mark I, the first ever IFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was withdrawn from action because it couldn't be used anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is a UOA pilot piloting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a total newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's leading the Secret to the Scub Coral!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.58,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Scub Coral?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If that thing destroys this, the island will be no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao, don't cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I dodged it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.81,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Trapar levels at 17mmol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that it can't see me because of trapar interference?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Alleluia. I've got visual on the Scub Coral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this trapar storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The third engine's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only function that the Mark I's researchers couldn't get working!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The third engine is working?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The IFO has two legs! It's standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel it! I feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the trapar wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not lost! Pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mark I was last confirmed to function 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okinawa was not yet independent at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The largest Scub Burst in history...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the pilot of the giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! His hair is turquoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,IFO! Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not broadcasting an international identification code.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirm your nationality and association.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:38.70,Alt,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not broadcasting an international identification code.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirm your nationality and association.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.71,0:17:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Elena. It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! He defeated the G-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. But I just know I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.33,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I guess you know about Generation Bleu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Though we don't specialize in rescuing kids floating on water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you hidden it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.04,0:19:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so we're gonna play that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.11,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Fleur Blanc. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.89,0:19:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukai Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukai Ao? What a simple name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.34,0:19:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That turquoise-haired kid is really that Fukai brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But what does GenBleu want from a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me the idol's hitting on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that seriously what you first think of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they're looking for that FP.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How about visiting the cave for old times' sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He caused a lot of trouble for the base! He piloted that giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, Mr Niigaki, you're a resident of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I work at the base. Think of me now as a man of the SDF.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to go out and look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just a normal child. There's no way he can pilot an IFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal? We have witnesses telling us that his hair was turquoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Turquoise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukai's kid Ao piloted the giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.75,0:21:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They said his hair was turquoise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That suspicious foreigner blew his cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We catch him before the SDF does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.25,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we have to resort to using force,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll make him spit out whether he got the giant from the Japs or from the UOA.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the sake of complete Okinawan independence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.10,0:21:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. We'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She said we mustn't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one place left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, including my dad, is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So are the SDF and the people from Generation Bleu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.72,0:22:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to protect the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not going to work out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a foreign kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it my fault that the monster showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ao...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.37,0:22:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm disgusting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it in my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair turned turquoise and you fought in the sea giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, a giant protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.22,0:23:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sea giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... This is Ao's sea giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To be continued.
